snippet.title: Jumpgate Evolution Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Scott Brown, the President of NetDevil, runs MMORPG.com through Jumpgate Evolution at GDC. In this video, he shows off Conflux Base and a Boss Fight.

http://www.mmorpg.com/
